msgid "[[!meta title=\"Closing tails-support@boum.org\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Tancament de tails-support@boum.org\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta date=\"Wed, 07 Jun 2017 12:34:56 +0000\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta date=\"Wed, 07 Jun 2017 12:34:56 +0000\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!pagetemplate template=\"news.tmpl\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We decided to close tails-support@boum.org, the public mailing list for user "
"support which [was created in 2013](https://tails.net/news/tails-support/)  "
"after closing the forum that we had on this website."
msgstr ""
"Hem decidit tancar tails-support@boum.org, la llista de correu pública per a "
"l'assistència als usuaris que [va ser creada el 2013](https://tails.net/news/"
"tails-support/index.ca.html) després de tancar el fòrum que teníem en aquest "
"lloc web."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "The idea behind having a public space for user support was to:"
msgstr ""
"La idea darrere de tenir un espai públic d'assistència als usuaris era:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Reduce the amount of work for our help desk behind [[tails-support-"
"private@boum.org|about/contact#tails-support-private]] (which is encrypted "
"and also receives [[*WhisperBack* reports|doc/first_steps/whisperback]])."
msgstr ""
"Reduir la quantitat de treball del nostre servei d'assistència [[tails-"
"support-private@boum.org|about/contact#tails-support-private]] (que està "
"encriptat i també rep [[informes de*WhisperBack*|doc/first_steps/"
"whisperback]])."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  This is not really working as tails-support-private@boum.org still\n"
"  has 12 times more traffic than tails-support@boum.org.\n"
msgstr ""
"  Això no funciona realment, ja que tails-support-private@boum.org encara\n"
"  té 12 vegades més trànsit que tails-support@boum.org.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Build a community of people doing user support outside of our team."
msgstr ""
"- Crear una comunitat de persones que fan suport als usuaris fora del nostre "
"equip."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  This is not really working either as most of the threads are still\n"
"  answered by our help desk or other core\n"
"  contributors.\n"
msgstr ""
"  Això tampoc funciona realment, ja que la majoria dels missatges encara estan\n"
"  sent contestats pel nostre servei d'ajuda o altres\n"
"  col·laboradors del nostre equip.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Build a public database to make it easy to consult or reuse previous "
"answers."
msgstr ""
"- Crear una base de dades pública per facilitar la consulta o la "
"reutilització de respostes anteriors."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  This is not really working either as the archive of the mailing list\n"
"  are hard to search and reuse and it's easier to point people to\n"
"  the documentation, known issues, or FAQ.\n"
msgstr ""
"  Això tampoc funciona realment ja que l'arxiu de la llista de correu\n"
"  és difícil de cercar i reutilitzar i és més fàcil apuntar a la gent a\n"
"  la documentació, als problemes coneguts o a les preguntes més freqüents.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Having a public mailing list also makes it:"
msgstr "Tenir una llista de correu pública també fa que:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Complicated to make sure that both the list and the sender receive our "
"answers."
msgstr ""
"Sigui complicat assegurar-nos que tant la llista com el remitent reben les "
"nostres respostes."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Sensitive to ask for more technical information about the problem, such as "
"logs, as they are harder for the person reporting the error to share with us "
"and also raises privacy concerns."
msgstr ""
"És sensible demanar més informació tècnica sobre el problema, com ara els "
"registres, ja que és més difícil que la persona que informa de l'error "
"comparteixi amb nosaltres i també planteja problemes de privadesa."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Duplicate work between tails-support-private@boum.org and tails-support@boum."
"org as people often write to both."
msgstr ""
"Duplica la feina entre tails-support-private@boum.org i tails-support@boum."
"org, ja que la gent sovint escriu a tots dos correus."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The major downside of closing tails-support@boum.org is that it was a good "
"place for developers to have some feedback on the recurrent problems faced "
"by users. We want to solve this while working on a [request tracker for our "
"help desk](https://tails.net/blueprint/RT_for_help_desk/)."
msgstr ""
"El principal inconvenient de tancar tails-support@boum.org és que era un bon "
"lloc perquè els desenvolupadors tinguessin comentaris sobre els problemes "
"recurrents als quals s'enfronten els usuaris. Volem resoldre això mentre "
"treballem en un [seguidor de sol·licituds per al nostre servei d'ajuda]"
"(https://tails.net/blueprint/RT_for_help_desk/)."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"See you on [[tails-support-private@boum.org|about/contact#tails-support-"
"private]]!"
msgstr ""
"Ens veiem a [[tails-support-private@boum.org|about/contact#tails-support-"
"private]]!"
